results.name: Pharrell x NMD Human Race 'Aqua'
results.story: Taken from a larger collection developed in partnership with the prolific artist, the Pharrell x adidas NMD Human Race ‘Aqua’ showcases monochromatic vibrant blue coloring throughout the sneaker’s exterior. Decorative laces are entwined within structural TPU cages that flank either side of the Primeknit upper, accented with tonal ‘Uluntu’ embroidery across the vamp. The minimalist build rests on a full-length Boost midsole in the same pastel finish.

results.name: Jordan 5 Retro Low Class of 2021
results.story: Releasing under the auspices of Jordan Brand’s Wings program, the Air Jordan 5 Retro Low Wings ‘Class of 2020-21’ pays tribute to a new crop of graduates. The low-top silhouette carries a formal all-black upper constructed from textile and nubuck. Metallic gold Jumpman branding on the tongue is matched by ‘20’ and ‘21’ embroidered on the lateral heel of each shoe. A lace adornment is made to resemble a graduation cap tassel, while a graphic on the sockliner draws inspiration from a diploma seal. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a matching black polyurethane midsole, accented with gold shark tooth detailing and supported by an icy translucent outsole.

results.name: Nike Cosmic Unity Ghost
results.story: The Nike Cosmic Unity ‘Ghost’ delivers a sleek colorway of a performance hoops shoe tasked with extending the brand’s ‘Move to Zero’ initiative. At least 25% recycled content goes into the composition of the futuristically styled upper, which encompasses the black cable yarn build, woven laces, and even the marbled blue Swoosh. A matching black finish is applied to the Crater Foam midsole, which works in tandem with a Zoom Air strobel to deliver springy cushioning and on-court responsiveness.

results.name: Cosmic Unity EP 'Ghost'
results.story: The Nike Cosmic Unity EP ‘Ghost’ updates the performance hoops shoe with a mostly black finish. The neutral palette is applied to the recycled cable yarn upper and Crater Foam midsole, which incorporates 10% Nike Grind Rubber. Nike’s sustainability efforts extend to the sneaker’s aesthetic and performance details, including the marbled blue Swoosh and full-length Zoom Air Strobel, both of which are partially composed of recycled content. This EP edition features an extra-durable rubber outsole for made for outdoor use.

results.name: ZX 6000 'Inside Out XZ 0006 Pack - Blue'
results.story: The adidas ZX 6000 ‘Blue’ is drawn from the three-piece ‘Inside Out XZ 0006 Pack,’ which revisits the unique inside-out design theme initially unveiled in the ‘A-ZX series.’ A vibrant shade of blue is applied to the textile upper, fortified with a semi-translucent toe wrap and an exposed-foam heel overlay. Coral-hued three-stripes adorn the quarter panel, while a standard adidas Trefoil graces the woven tongue tag. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a beige EVA midsole, accented with an unexpected pop of wraparound pink detailing.

results.name: Keith Haring x Chuck Taylor All Star Low
Wmns Waffle One 'Fuchsia Gold'
results.story: The Nike women’s Waffle One ‘Fuchsia Gold’ showcases vibrant hues on a retro-inspired silhouette that carries on the legacy of the iconic waffle franchise. The ventilated upper pairs transparent mesh with contrasting suede overlays in lavender and orange. The latter hue is repeated on the leather Swoosh and TPU heel clip, featuring an angled topline that merges with the wedge-shaped foam midsole. Underfoot, Nike’s waffle traction rubber outsole provides optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Waffle One 'Black White'
results.story: The Nike women’s Waffle One ‘Black White’ delivers an essential two-tone colorway of the lifestyle runner that seamlessly blends old and new. Similar to the DBreak-Type, the upper is constructed from transparent mesh with suede overlays at the toe and heel. The all-black finish is disrupted by a white leather Swoosh and matching branding elements atop the molded tongue. A pronounced TPU heel clip is integrated into the dual-stacked foam midsole, rendered in a classic wedge shape and supported by a waffle-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Keith Haring x Pro Leather Low
Air Force 1 Crater Flyknit 'Black Chambray Blue'
Keith Haring x Run Star Hike
LeBron 18 'Black White Gum'
results.story: The Nike LeBron 18 ‘Black White Gum’ delivers an essential colorway of LeBron James’ 18th signature shoe. A solid black finish is applied to the Knitposite 2.0 upper, featuring integrated lacing and a contrasting white TPU heel counter covered in speckled detailing. The sneaker’s innovative cushioning setup features Cushlon foam and full-length Zoom Air that’s partially housed within a large-volume Max Air unit nestled in the heel. Underfoot, a gum rubber outsole uses a grid-like traction pattern for maximum grip.

results.name: Waffle One 'Electric Green'
results.story: The Nike Waffle One ‘Electric Green’ applies a lush hue to a lifestyle silhouette inspired by the Swoosh’s running heritage. Breathable comfort is provided by a semi-translucent mesh upper, accented with a black leather Swoosh and bolstered by tonal suede overlays at the toe and heel. A thin, low-cut collar allows for flexibility and a full range of motion, while a TPU heel clip delivers rearfoot stability. Springy cushioning comes courtesy of a Phylon midsole, rendered in a classic wedge shape and reinforced by Nike’s iconic waffle outsole.

results.name: Cardi B x Wmns Club C 'Rose Gold'
Nike Kobe 5 Protro Undefeated Hall of Fame
results.story: The Undefeated x Nike Zoom Kobe 5 Protro ‘Hall of Fame’ celebrates Kobe Bryant’s induction into the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame. As a nod to the Mamba’s championship pedigree, a metallic gold finish coats the upper, crafted from breathable mesh with snakeskin-textured leather overlays. Each shoe is accented with a purple Swoosh on the right side panel and a mismatched pink Swoosh on the left. Specific to the left shoe, the pink Swoosh is inscribed with the numbers 24, 10 and 8, representing the jersey numbers that Kobe wore with the Lakers and Team USA. Additional mismatched branding lands on the tongue and heel, both featuring Kobe’s personal trademark and Undefeated’s Five Strikes logo.

results.name: Jordan 1 Retro AJKO Chicago (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Air Jordan 1 KO ‘Chicago’ brings back an OG colorway initially released in 1986 and last reissued in 2014. Like the original, the high-top features a white canvas upper with contrasting red canvas on the eyestay and forefoot overlay. Black leather is utilized on the signature Swoosh and padded collar, overlaid with red leather flaps that display an AJKO Wings logo on the lateral side. Tooling is reminiscent of the Nike Vandal, complete with encapsulated Air sole cushioning and a circular traction pattern on the rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan Why Not Zer0.4 PF 'KB3'
results.story: The Jordan Why Not Zer0.4 ‘KB3 PF showcases an airy build on Russell Westbrook’s fourth signature shoe. The sneaker makes use of a slate blue mesh upper, accented with lavender webbing straps integrated into the lacing system for a lockdown fit. Responsive cushioning arrives via double-stacked Air Zoom units nestled in the forefoot of the full-length foam midsole. This PF version is exclusive to the Asian market and features an extra-durable rubber outsole made for play on outdoor courts.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam More v3 'White UV Glow'
Nike Dunk SB Low Stingwater Magic Mushroom
results.story: Developed in partnership with Daniel Kim’s skate brand, the Stingwater x Nike Dunk Low SB ‘Magic Mushroom’ makes use of a crimson leather upper with safari-print overlays meant to resemble the surface of a mushroom cap. On the lateral quarter panel, a small jewel Swoosh is joined by an embroidered and partially scrambled ‘Stingwater’ wordmark. Reverse ‘Nike’ branding adorns the heel tab, while the tongue features a zippered stash pocket and a woven interior tag inscribed with ‘Free Your Mind’ in the same inverted lettering. Underfoot, the translucent rubber outsole reveals printed text on each shoe that reads ‘Plant Emoji’ and ‘With Eyes.’

adidas Yeezy 500 Enflame
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 500 ‘Enflame’ spotlights the sneaker’s adiPRENE+ tooling with a vibrant orange finish. Offering a blend of impact absorption and responsive cushioning, the podular midsole is directly inspired by the adidas KB8 3, released in 1999 as Kobe Bryant’s third signature shoe. Up top, the sneaker’s complex build combines brown open mesh with soft suede overlays in tan, grey and indigo. A rubber midfoot wrap provides added durability and support.

results.name: Wmns FuelCell Rebel v2 Wide 'Black White Mint'
Kyrie 7 EP 'Daybreak'
results.story: The Nike Kyrie 7 EP ‘Daybreak’ features a pale violet mesh upper with a unique flaming Swoosh in red and yellow. Contrasting pastel green accents land on the tongue and midsole, which houses a large forefoot Air Zoom Turbo unit for extra-responsive cushioning in all directions. Additional performance benefits include a padded collar for Achilles support and molded fins integrated into the laces for a lockdown fit. Underfoot, a bright yellow rubber outsole features a 360-degree computer-generated traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns FuelCell Rebel v2 'White Virtual Sky'
Wmns FuelCell Rebel v2 Wide 'White Mint'
Kamikaze 2 Low OG 'Black White' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Reebok Kamikaze 2 Low OG ‘Black White’ brings back the original 1996 colorway of the hoops shoe made famous by Seattle legend Shawn Kemp. Rendered in low-top form, the sneaker carries a black nubuck upper with dynamic white leather overlays across each side panel, featuring aggressive lines that extend to the matching black-and-white EVA midsole. Underfoot, cutaway detailing on the rubber outsole reveals Reebok’s Hexalite cushioning technology.

results.name: Air Jordan 7 Retro TD 'Flint' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Air Jordan 7 Retro TD ‘Flint’ brings back the 2006 colorway in toddler sizing. A webbing pull tab at the heel allows for easy entry into an upper crafted from grey nubuck and white synthetic leather. ‘Jordan’ is inscribed in violet lettering on the plush tongue, matching an embroidered Jumpman on the collar and ‘23’ branding on the heel. The sneaker sits atop a soft foam midsole, supported underfoot by a durable rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 7 Retro Flint (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 7 Retro ‘Flint’ brings back a mostly neutral colorway that originally released in 2006. The mid-top silhouette features a dark grey suede upper with tumbled white leather overlays throughout. Contrasting purple accents make their way to the branding elements, which include a Jumpman logo on the lateral collar and ‘23’ embossed on the geometric heel patch. Sharp angles reoccur on the seamless tongue and polyurethane midsole, enhanced with encapsulated Nike Air cushioning under the heel.

results.name: MTA X 992 Made In England 'NYC Subway'
results.story: Launching exclusively at Dover Street Market, the MTA x New Balance 920 Made In England ‘NYC Subway’ pays homage to New York’s public transportation agency. Inspired by New Balance’s 900 and 1000 series, the 920 is assembled in the brand’s Flimby factory and features a grey open mesh upper with tonal pigskin suede overlays. MTA branding lands on the back heel and custom sockliner, while mismatched lace jewels display the Union Jack and the Stars and Stripes. The sneaker rides on a two-tone ENCAP midsole that combines soft EVA cushioning with a tough polyurethane rim.

results.name: Wmns FuelCell Rebel v2 Wide 'White Virtual Sky'
Air Jordan 7 Retro GS 'Flint' 2021
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Air Jordan 7 Retro GS ‘Flint’ brings back a 2006 colorway in big kid sizing. The mid-top makes use of a grey nubuck upper with white tumbled leather overlays and a Huarache-like inner sleeve for a snug, comfortable fit. Court Purple accents make their way to Air Jordan lettering on the tongue, an embroidered Jumpman on the lateral collar and a raised ‘23’ on the angular heel patch. The sneaker rides on a foam midsole with Nike Air cushioning in the heel for improved impact protection.
